Package: pnardl
Type: Package
Title: Panel Nonlinear ARDL Estimation
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: person("Muhammad", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: Implements the Panel Nonlinear Autoregressive Distributed Lag
    (PNARDL) model following Shin, Yu and Greenwood-Nimmo (2014)
    <doi:10.1007/978-1-4899-8008-3_9>. The method decomposes regressors into
    positive and negative partial sums to capture asymmetric long-run and
    short-run effects. Supports Pooled Mean Group (PMG), Mean Group (MG), and
    Dynamic Fixed Effects (DFE) estimators via within-group OLS. Includes
    asymmetry Wald tests, dynamic multipliers, and impulse response functions
    for positive versus negative shocks.
